<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hustlerati | Commercial Space Rental Platform</title>
    <meta name="description"
        content="Find, compare, and rent commercial spaces tailored to your business needs anytime, anywhere in the world.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="commercial space rental, business space, retail space, warehouse rental, industrial space,
        restaurant space, office space, commercial real estate, business solutions, Hustlerati">
    <meta name="author" content="Hustlerati Team">
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/logo.png" type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/images/logo.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/default.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body class="light-theme">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="hero-content">
                    <h2>Hustle Remotely with <span class="highlight">Hustlerati</span>,
                        The Right Commercial Space for Your Business</h2>
                    <p>Find, compare, and rent commercial spaces tailored to your business needs anytime, anywhere in
                        the world - from small retail stores to large industrial warehouses. Find your space and let
                        Hustlerati handle the rest! Hustle smarter, not harder.</p>
                    <div class="search-bar">
                        <div class="hero-actions" style="display: flex; gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                            <a href="/real_estate" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">
                                <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i> Get Started
                            </a>
                            <a href="/shop" class="btn btn-secondary btn-large">
                                <i class="fas fa-shopping-bag"></i> Shop with Hustlerati
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hero-tags">
                        <span>Popular Searches:</span>
                        <a href="/real_estate">Retail Space Nairobi</a>
                        <a href="/real_estate">Warehouse Mombasa</a>
                        <a href="/real_estate">Industrial Space Kisumu</a>
                        <a href="/real_estate">Restaurant Space Dubai</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-image">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600585152220-90363fe7e115?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1470&q=80"
                        alt="Commercial Space">
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="how-it-works">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>How It Works</h2>
                <div class="steps">
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Step 1</h3>
                        <p>Find a space that meets your needs</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Step 2</h3>
                        <p>Show interest by adding your name to the list of interested parties</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-credit-card"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Step 3</h3>
                        <p>Rent the space on a first come(pay) first serve basis</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-usd"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Step 4</h3>
                        <p>Don't have enough money? Hustlerati has you covered</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Step 5</h3>
                        <p>Join the Hustlerati Community full of people like you, let Hustlerati help you pool your
                            resources and get the space you need</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Step 6</h3>
                        <p>Hustlerati is a democratic platform for the people, by the people, with the people</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-coins"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Step 7</h3>
                        <p>Earn democratically as per your contribution</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="cta-card">
                    <h3>Ready to Find Your Perfect Commercial Space?</h3>
                    <p>Join thousands of businesses that found their ideal location through Hustlerati</p>
                    <div class="cta-buttons">
                        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Find Space</button>
                        <a href="/list-your-estate"><button class="btn btn-outline btn-large">List Your
                                Property</button></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/javascript/localization.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascript/accessibility.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascript/index.js"></script>
</body>

</html>